    "description": "Join the Imperial Logistics India South Asia Partners family as a Supply Chain Manager in Thane. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Imperial Logistics India South Asia Partners:\nImperial Logistics India South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Thane, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Imperial Logistics India South Asia Partners!",
